 [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.5279}, {"x": 0.8928, "y": 0.5279}, {"x": 0.8928, "y": 0.8205}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.8205}], "comment": "Strong use of comparative survival statistics demonstrates concrete improvement. Including a note on sample size or research design would further assess evidence reliability.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "dab162d6-39d5-4b1e-80cc-594b99af180b", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.5156, "width": 0.7726999999999999, "height": 0.09710000000000008}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.5156}, {"x": 0.8854, "y": 0.5156}, {"x": 0.8854, "y": 0.6127}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.6127}], "comment": "The citation \u00e2\u0080\u009cSchuller, 2022\u00e2\u0080\u009d is appropriate, but the student might briefly assess the source\u00e2\u0080\u0099s credibility to reinforce the reliability of the evidence provided.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "9a765a3c-6ae7-47fb-9e83-efeb52cfc7aa", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.4176, "width": 0.739, "height": 0.0923}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.4176}, {"x": 0.8517, "y": 0.4176}, {"x": 0.8517, "y": 0.5099}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.5099}], "comment": "The background on cancer\u00e2\u0080\u0099s history is informative but would benefit from linking to TOK concepts like paradigm shifts in medical knowledge or the role of peer review in validating treatments.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "f75dcfde-bfec-4168-a608-b3bdddfe0a23", "versionId"