as \u00e2\u0080\u009cimprovement.\u00e2\u0080\u009d", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "ddabb084-530d-4f97-9512-ee2eeaee44e4", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.8527, "width": 0.7592, "height": 0.05399999999999994}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.8527}, {"x": 0.8719, "y": 0.8527}, {"x": 0.8719, "y": 0.9067}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.9067}], "comment": "The conclusion reiterates earlier points without addressing possible limitations of current calculators (e.g. overreliance on technology). Considering counter-arguments would add nuance.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "eeaef851-90d0-4bf6-a756-3a0c20f808e9", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "general", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0928, "width": 0.7402, "height": 0.018000000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0928}, {"x": 0.8529, "y": 0.0928}, {"x": 0.8529, "y": 0.1108}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.1108}], "comment": "The criterion for \u00e2\u0080\u009cimprovement\u00e2\u0080\u009d is assumed to be practical benefit; defining explicit standards (accuracy, ethical considerations, epistemic values) would make the analysis more precise.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "8d136c42-f971-4308-af11-7bef2226ba14", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1195, "y": 0.1449, "width": 0.4442, "height": 0.2538}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1195, "y": 0.1449}, {"x": 0.5637, "y": 0.1449}, {"x": 0.5637, "y": 0.3987}, {"x": 0.1195, "y": 0.3987}], "comment": "The micrograph visually emphasizes the scientific context. A brief comment on how imaging technologies shape interpretation could enrich the TOK analysis.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "ed435477-f3ae-44a6-86d0-1eb4a13d60c6", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.8385, "width": 0.7782, "height": 0.03739999999999999}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.8385}, {"x": 0.8909, "y": 0.8385}, {"x": 0.8909, "y": 0.8759}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.8759}], "comment": "Invoking the scientific method is valid, but the analysis of specific stages (hypothesis testing, peer review) is missing. Explicitly linking methods to knowledge refinement would deepen the argument.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "810fb287-7f38-4d1a-8b92-602fe2e930f6", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0928, "width": 0.3842, "height": 0.018000000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0928}, {"x": 0.4969, "y": 0.0928}, {"x": 0.4969, "y": 0.1108}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.1108}], "comment": "Identifying the personal calculator adds originality and connects theory to the student\u00e2\u0080\u0099s own experience, strengthening the real-world context.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "773c172d-3b55-45e7-9157-7ffae694c43e", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.5606, "width": 0.7757999999999999, "height": 0.2732}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.5606}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.5606}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.8338}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.8338}], "comment": "The historical comparison with the abacus effectively shows progress. To enhance this, the student could discuss how changing definitions of \u00e2\u0080\u009caccuracy\u00e2\u0080\u009d reflect shifting knowledge standards.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "cfc221d8-9538-4a95-ac4b-b469697bb661", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1189, "y": 0.1297, "width": 0.2757, "height": 0.2813}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1189, "y": 0.1297}, {"x": 0.3946, "y": 0.1297}, {"x": 0.3946, "y": 0.411}, {"x": 0.1189, "y": 0.411}], "comment": "The embedded function could be rendered in LaTeX (e.g. $$f(x)=x^3$$) to align with academic standards and precision in mathematical notation.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "6f7b145f-83e3-41e8-9893-498e24103d7a", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "general", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0928, "width": 0.7402, "height": 0.018000000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0928}, {"x": 0.8529, "y": 0.0928}, {"x": 0.8529, "y": 0.1108}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.1108}], "comment": "Overall, the exhibition shows coherent object selection and evidence, but it would benefit from explicit use of TOK vocabulary (e.g. reliability, validity, justification) to develop a more sophisticated argument.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "e96ce633-9fae-451d-aeb7-cd986798ff58", "versionId": "9ebf4a42-5806-4678-a55a-a787fffdab2c", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "general", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0928, "width": 0.7402, "height": 0.018000000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0928}, {"x": 0.8529, "y": 0.0928}, {"x": 0.8529, "y": 0.1108}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.1108}], "comment": "Consider introducing counter-examples or scenarios where current knowledge might introduce new challenges, to avoid a purely progressive narrative and demonstrate critical balance.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}]}]}}, "rubricData": {"id": 57, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "version": 1, "status": "published", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:43.512632+00", "totalMarks": 10, "description": null, "type": "TOK", "rubricSpecificInfo": null, "tags": [""], "isArchived": false, "gradeBoundaryId": "52ad2701-27bc-42f3-be3f-d63b98d98139", "name": "TOK Exhibition", "slug": "tok-exhibition", "rubricCriteria": [{"id": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "revisionId": 57, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition", "label": null, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:55.358727+00", "updatedAt": "2025-07-16 11:21:18.828885+00", "isGradable": true, "showGradedScore": true, "isChecklistCriterion": false, "description": null, "rubricCriterionBands": [{"id": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 0, "marksTo": 0, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:46.486581+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f7cb0652-0737-403e-8f65-be13bd2fd7f1", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "content": "The exhibition does not reach the standard described by the other levels or does not use one of the IA prompts provided.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:58.577216+00"}]}, {"id": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 1, "marksTo": 2, "orderIndex": 1, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:47.076074+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "861f06ce-2b51-46ce-a6ee-3022e7080288", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "content": "The exhibition presents\nthree objects, but the\nreal-world contexts of\nthese objects are not\nstated, or the images\npresented may be\nhighly generic images of\ntypes of object rather\nthan of specific\nreal-world objects. Links\nbetween the objects\nand the selected IA\nprompt are made, but\nthese are minimal,\ntenuous, or it is not\nclear what the student is\ntrying to convey.\nThere is very little\njustification offered for\nthe inclusion of each\nobject in the exhibition.\nThe commentary on the\nobjects is highly\ndescriptive or consists\nonly of unsupported\nassertions.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:04.443183+00"}]}, {"id": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 3, "marksTo": 4, "orderIndex": 2, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.072006+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "e8acd337-a77d-4319-a744-06094151d57b", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of the objects may be implied rather than explicitly stated. Basic links between the objects and the selected IA prompt are made, but the explanation of these links is unconvincing and/or unfocused. There is a superficial justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Reasons for the inclusion of the objects are offered, but these are not supported by appropriate evidence and/or lack relevance to the selected IA prompt. There may be significant repetition across the justifications of the different objects", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:20.428881+00"}]}, {"id": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 5, "marksTo": 6, "orderIndex": 3, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.868343+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "c257e18a-e3b8-46f4-b3b9-d9ea5cd5db84", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of these objects may be vaguely or imprecisely stated. There is some explanation of the links between the three objects and the selected IA prompt. There is some justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Some of the points are supported by evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:31.312862+00"}]}, {"id": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 7, "marksTo": 8, "orderIndex": 4, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:49.555746+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f16fe76e-abd8-4dc1-9a4f-50ab9e121c99", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects and their real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are explained, although this explanation may lack precision and clarity in parts. There is a justification of the contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. Many of the points are supported by appropriate evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:40.123527+00"}]}, {"id": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 9, "marksTo": 10, "orderIndex": 5, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:50.346899+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "055fe2ad-3ef1-4074-af44-83cc3440cc7a", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "content": "The exhibition clearly identifies three objects and their specific real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are clearly made and well-explained. There is a strong justification of the particular contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. All, or nearly all, of the points are well-supported by appropriate evidence and explicit references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:51.46084+00"}]}], "rubricCriterionStrands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:59.452498+00", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?"}]}]}, "similarExemplars": [{"id": "e3360e2f-ad1c-4181-b94e-a2eca2ea86e3", "title": "How can we know that current knowledge is an improvement upon past knowledge?", "description": "", "tags": ["grade-B", "tok", "sl"], "slug": "how-can-we-know-that-current-knowledge-is-an-improvement", "isPublic": true, "isPremium": true, "showScores": true, "createdAt": "2025-08-05T07:49:28.485Z", "userSubmissionId": "4db77bdb-d27c-4302-a66c-8965d9807aa5", "submissionId": "c4775670-bd5b-418c-9e47-ba21e7367ef1", "similarity": 0.5686537819999999, "normalizedScore": 0.8, "compositeScore": 0.6380576473999999, "matchingFileId": "", "matchingChunkId": "", "matchingChunkNumber": 0, "userSubmission": {"id":